sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant D as DNS
    participant L as Azure Load Balancer
    participant F as App Service Frontend
    participant W as Worker Instance
    participant A as App Process

    C->>D: Resolve host name
    D-->>C: IP address / CNAME target
    C->>L: HTTPS request
    L->>F: Forward inbound traffic
    F->>F: TLS termination + SNI/Host validation
    F->>F: Access restriction evaluation
    F->>W: Route to healthy instance
    W->>A: Reverse proxy to app port
    A-->>W: Generate response
    W-->>F: Return upstream response
    F-->>L: Add platform headers / egress
    L-->>C: HTTP response
